The global homeopathy products market is expected to witness significant growth by 2028. The market is segmented by source into plants, animals, and minerals. Among these, the plant-based segment is anticipated to hold a substantial market share due to the increasing preference for natural remedies. In terms of types, the market is categorized into tinctures, dilutions, biochemics, ointments, and tablets. The dilutions segment is expected to show considerable growth owing to its easy consumption and higher efficacy. Furthermore, based on applications, the market is segmented into respiratory, neurology, immunology, dermatology, and others. The respiratory segment is projected to dominate the market due to the rising prevalence of respiratory disorders. When it comes to distribution channels, pharmacies, online retailers, and direct sales are the key segments. The online retailers segment is expected to witness significant growth with the increasing trend of e-commerce platforms.

