The application of homeopathy products spans across various therapeutic areas, including respiratory, neurology, immunology, dermatology, and others. The respiratory segment is expected to lead the market, driven by the increasing incidence of respiratory disorders such as asthma, bronchitis, and allergies. Homeopathy offers alternative treatment options for respiratory conditions, appealing to individuals seeking natural and non-invasive approaches to managing their health. Additionally, the neurology and dermatology segments are also poised for growth, as homeopathy products gain recognition for their effectiveness in addressing neurological disorders and skin conditions.

